Indulge in a remarkable blend of contemporary elegance and personalized potential with this exquisite 2-bedroom, 2.5-bath townhome in Tampa, Florida. Adorned with luxurious granite countertops and sleek hardwood flooring on the lower level, while offering plush carpeting upstairs, this residence stands as a pristine canvas awaiting your unique touch. Set in one of the United States' most beloved living destinations, relish in Tampa's alluring lifestyle – from its renowned beaches to its cultural treasures and culinary delights.
